{"tid":2254497,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星島賣盤交易現變數","createTime":"2020-10-23T01:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T01:20:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15fc642b6d04f42265e529878d2f056f0270ebca","tid":2254497,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201023/JP5RUZUZ4NBL5GME2EGVBGXK64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201023%2FJP5RUZUZ4NBL5GME2EGVBGXK64%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRL500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=d6c0954d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201023%2FJP5RUZUZ4NBL5GME2EGVBGXK64%2F&h=0942779d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201023/JP5RUZUZ4NBL5GME2EGVBGXK64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n星島賣盤交易現變數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i5gDwIDowUmszFQt7Aa0RPsDTBI=/1280x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IM7A5PCFDZEDDBQWM42RGNGFII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi5gDwIDowUmszFQt7Aa0RPsDTBI%3D%2F1280x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIM7A5PCFDZEDDBQWM42RGNGFII.jpg&h=56b2b76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■星島主席何柱國。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】星島（1105）就其早前賣盤事宜發出更新公告，指買賣雙方已要求、而監管機構亦已授予撤回就取得監管機構之批准的通知，意味交易出現變數；主席何柱國、潛在買家及其各自之法律顧問，現正就該撤回商議有關潛在交易的可行替代安排。星島股價昨下跌0.88%，報1.12元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n研撤回交易替代安排<br />\n<br />\n星島指，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上月星島曾指，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n星島上半年虧損增加至6,129萬元，收入為4億元，按年跌36%。公司指整個媒體行業受疫情侵襲而陷入「冰河時期」，於嚴峻的營商環境中，集團媒體之經營業績出現倒退。"},{"pid":"a260aaf5267f2df59fe8ccd1963e1f39fea25aba","tid":2254497,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"呢個年代除咗果班急住要同支共表忠嘅奶共商人之外 仲會有乜嘢人會拎億